126-#### Finding 1 - Critical - A two-Director route can collapse to one distinct Director
127-
128-`ConflictOfInterestModule.effective_approvers` replaces excluded Director 1 with Director 2, then
129-appends Director 2 again when it reaches that actor's original slot. `authority_is_satisfiable`
130-compares list lengths rather than exact distinct role/user counts, while final completion converts
131-the list to a user-id set. A CFO + two-Director route can therefore be marked satisfiable and
132-sanctioned by only CFO + one distinct Director. The executable review probe produced three slots
133-but only two distinct user ids. This violates auth §§16.2/27.1, security §12, and codebase-design
134-§13.1's all-required-approvals invariant. `007E2` owns distinct replacement and blocked ledgers.
